Interface CloseableIterator<E>

All Known Implementing Classes:
sailpoint.connector.AbstractObjectIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.DelimitedContentsIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.FileContentsIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.PartitionIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.RegExSingleLinedIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.RegExSortedMultiLinedIterator, DelimitedFileConnector.RegExUnSortedMultiLinedIterator, JDBCConnector.JDBCObjectIterator
public interface CloseableIterator<E>

Similar to the Iterator interface, but with an additional CloseableIterator.close() method that can clean up resources when the iteration is complete. This also does not have a remove() method.
